.sales-section.large {
  padding: var(--space-24) 0;
}

/* Alternating background colors for visual separation */
.sales-section:nth-child(even) {
  background: var(--gray-50);
}
```

### Content Spacing
```css
.sales-content {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-6);
}

.sales-content > * + * {
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
